The film focuses on the frontline of Wuhan's fight against the epidemic, with Wuhan medical staff and medical teams from various provinces and cities as the background, from the perspective of human nature, using a unique narrative and a highly impactful lens language, to show the touching stories of Chinese medical workers full of dedication and sacrifice on the front line of the epidemic.
